        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 1,
            "text": "The Striking Event"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 2,
            "text": "What is the Striking Event"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 3,
            "text": "And what may let you know what the Striking Event is"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 4,
            "text": "(It will happen) on a day when people will be like scattered moths"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "and the mountains will be like carded wool"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "Then, as for him whose scales (of good deeds) are heavy"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "he will be in a happy life"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "But he whose scales are light"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "his abode will be Abyss"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "And what may let you know what that (Abyss) is"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 101,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "A blazing Fire"
        }
    ]
}